meta.content: MaryMagdalene - Exploring Medieval Mary Magdalene (and More) Online Project Description The goal of this project is of a twofold nature: in terms of research results, it will create an interactive online edition of a medieval Mary Magdalene legend transmitted in the Lower Rhine area; in terms of teaching practice, it will train graduate and undergraduate students in palaeography, editing, and coding.

<pb edRef="#B1" facs="#B1_186r"/> <ab>
<ab xml:id="legend_title">Dyt is dat leven der seliger <name type="person" nymRef="Mary_Magdalene">marien <choice><abbr>magdalene̅</abbr><expan>magdalenen</expan></choice></name></ab><lb/>
<ab xml:id="genealogy"><name rend="underline" type="person" nymRef="Mary_Magdalene"><hi rend="init_lombard">M</hi>aria magdalena</name> was geboeren van<lb/>
edelem <choice><abbr>stam<am>̅</am>e</abbr><expan>stam<ex>m</ex>e</expan></choice> van eyme <choice><abbr>errliche̅</abbr><expan>errlichen</expan></choice><lb/>

geslecht van der stat <name rend="underline" type="place" nymRef="Jerusalem"><choice><abbr>jhrlm͂</abbr><expan>Jherusalem</expan></choice></name><pc resp="editor">.</pc> Ir vader heysch <name rend="underline" type="person" nymRef="Syrus">Cerus</name><lb/>
ir moder <name rend="underline" type="person" nymRef="Eucharia">Eucharia</name> Ind sy hatten zwae <choice><abbr>docht<am>̛</am></abbr><expan>docht<ex>er</ex></expan></choice> ind<lb/>

eynen son<pc source="manuscript">.</pc> de <choice><abbr>ey̅</abbr><expan>eyn</expan></choice> <choice><abbr>docht<am>̛</am></abbr><expan>docht<ex>er</ex></expan></choice> heisch <name rend="underline" type="person" nymRef="Mary_Magdalene"><choice><abbr>m<am>͂</am></abbr><expan>m<ex>aria</ex></expan>
</choice></name><pc source="manuscript">,</pc> de ander <name rend="underline" type="person" nymRef="Martha">martha</name><lb/>
ind der son heisch <name rend="underline" type="person" nymRef="Lazarus">lazarus</name> und der was den unse <name type="person" nymRef="Jesus_Christ">here</name> up<lb/>
erweckde van deme dode<pc resp="editor">.</pc></ab><ab xml:id="heritage">Ind na deme dode<lb/>
yrre alderen deylten de kynder ir vederliche ervve<pc resp="editor">.</pc><lb/>

<name rend="underline" type="person" nymRef="Lazarus">lazarus</name> nam <choice><abbr>ey̅</abbr><expan>eyn</expan></choice> groesse deyl in der stat van <name rend="underline" type="place" nymRef="Jerusalem"><choice><abbr>jhrlm͂</abbr><expan>Jherusalem</expan></choice></name> <subst><del rend="strikethrough" place="above">an</del><lb/><add><unclear>in</unclear></add></subst>

<choice><abbr>id̅</abbr><expan>ind</expan></choice> oiffde sych in der <choice><abbr>ritt<am>̛</am>schaff</abbr><expan>ritt<ex>er</ex>schaff</expan></choice> want he was <choice><abbr>ey̅</abbr><expan>eyn</expan></choice> <choice><abbr>ritt<am>̛</am></abbr><expan>ritt<ex>er</ex></expan></choice><pc resp="editor">.</pc> <name rend="underline" type="person" nymRef="Martha">martha</name><lb/>
geloeffde dem <name type="person" nymRef="Jesus_Christ">heren</name> zo denen in reynicht Ind<lb/>
wart eyn herbrigeirrersche der <choice><abbr>pylgrime̅</abbr><expan>pylgrimen</expan></choice> Ind <choice><abbr>sunderliche̅</abbr><expan>sunderlichen</expan></choice><pc resp="editor">.</pc><lb/>
umb irs h<pc source="manuscript">.</pc> levens wylle was sy wurdich zo herbrichen<lb/>

unssen heren <name rend="underline" type="person" nymRef="Jesus_Christ"><choice><abbr>jhm͂ ꭓm</abbr><expan>ihesum Christum</expan></choice></name> syn l<pc source="manuscript">.</pc> moder Ind de apostelen<pc resp="editor">.</pc> Ind ir<lb/>

ander deyl was dat stetgen <name rend="underline" type="place" nymRef="Bethany">bethania</name> gelegen na by <name rend="underline" type="place" nymRef="Jerusalem"><choice><abbr>jhrlm͂</abbr><expan>Jherusalem</expan></choice></name><lb/>
Ind wat ihr overquam van eren rentten dat gaff sy den ar<lb/>

men umb gotz wyllen<pc resp="editor">.</pc> <name rend="underline" type="person" nymRef="Mary_Magdalene">maria </name>nam zo <choice><abbr>ire̅</abbr><expan>iren</expan></choice> <choice><abbr>ey̅</abbr><expan>eyn</expan></choice> deyl dat<lb/>

sloss <name type="place" subtype="residence" nymRef="magdalum"><choice><abbr>magdalu̅</abbr><expan><ex>magdalum</ex></expan></choice></name> Ind da van hatte sy den namen <name type="person" rend="underline" nymRef="Mary_Magdalene"><choice><abbr>magdale<am>̅</am>a</abbr><expan><ex>magdalena</ex></expan></choice></name><pc resp="editor">.</pc></ab><lb/>
<ab xml:id="MaryMagdalene_mismanagement">Ind alle ir goit braicht sy zo in groessen swaren <choice><abbr>su̅den</abbr><expan>sunden</expan></choice><lb/>
myt boessen geselschaff Ind der boesse geist braicht sy zo<lb/>

va<subst><del rend="strikethrough" place="above">ne</del><add><unclear>ll</unclear></add></subst>zo manchen <choice><abbr>su̅den</abbr><expan>sunden</expan></choice><pc source="manuscript">,</pc> zo dem erster mayl in <unclear><choice><abbr>hoverdei<am>̅</am>e</abbr><expan>hoverdei<ex>ne</ex></expan></choice></unclear><lb/>
want sy was houerdich van hertzen dat ir doicht dat<lb/>
ir nemant gelich en was in <choice><abbr>schoy<am>̅</am>heit</abbr><expan>schoy<ex>n</ex>heit</expan></choice><pc resp="editor">.</pc> Ouch so was sy<lb/>
</ab><pb/>
<pb edRef="#B1" facs="#B1_186v"/>

<ab><choice><abbr>hov<am>̛</am>dich</abbr><expan>hov<ex>er</ex>dich</expan></choice> in worden Ind in wercken myt <choice><abbr>cleyd<am>ȇ</am>n</abbr><expan>cleyde<ex>re</ex>n</expan></choice> myt<lb/>
zerrheit yrs lychams<pc resp="editor">.</pc> Sy was ouch gyrich van zijt<lb/>
lichen dyngen<pc source="manuscript">.</pc> got und ere<pc source="manuscript">.</pc> Und waillust der werelt<pc resp="editor">.</pc> Ouch<lb/>
was sy <subst> <del rend="strikethrough">gyrich</del> <add>unkuisch</add></subst> van worden Ind wercken<pc source="manuscript">.</pc> also<lb/>
dat sy ere goit geruicht verlorre Ind yren <choice><abbr>eygene̅</abbr><expan>eygenen</expan></choice><choice><abbr>name̅</abbr><expan>namen</expan></choice><lb/>
Ind ouch also swerrlichen dat sy <choice><abbr>ey̅</abbr><expan>eyn</expan></choice> offenbare <choice><abbr>su̅dery̅ne</abbr><expan>sunderynne</expan></choice><lb/>

wart genant<pc resp="editor">.</pc></ab> Als ouch spricht <name type="person" nymRef="Luke">Lucas</name> der <choice><abbr>ewa̅gelista</abbr><expan>ewangelista</expan></choice><pc source="manuscript">,</pc> <choice><abbr>wa̅t</abbr><expan>want</expan></choice><lb/>

sy <choice><abbr>su̅tge</abbr><expan>suntge</expan></choice> de swerrlich myt yrme gesijcht<pc resp="editor">.</pc> Ir <choice><abbr>sust<am>̛</am></abbr><expan>sust<ex>er</ex></expan></choice> <name rend="underline" type="person" nymRef="Martha">martha</name><lb/>

claigde dat <choice><abbr>leve̅</abbr><expan>leven</expan></choice> yrre <choice><abbr>sust<am>̛</am></abbr><expan>sust<ex>er</ex></expan></choice> der <name type="person" nymRef="Virgin_Mary">moder</name><name rend="underline" type="person" nymRef="Jesus_Christ">christi</name> myt <choice><abbr>schrye̅<abbr>de̅</abbr></abbr><expan>schryenden</expan></choice><lb/>
ougen Ind batte sy dat sy den <name type="person" nymRef="Jesus_Christ">heren</name> vur sy woulde bydden<pc resp="editor">.</pc><lb/>
<ab xml:id="Martha_confronts_Mary"> Der leirre <name type="person" nymRef= "Pseudo_Isidore" >ysidorus</name> spricht<pc source="manuscript">,</pc> dat dese susteren quamen<lb/>

zo samen zo <name type="place" nymRef="Bethany">bethanien</name><pc resp="editor">.</pc> Ind <name rend="underline" type="person" nymRef="Mary_Magdalene"><choice><abbr>m<am>͂</am></abbr><expan>m<ex>aria</ex></expan>
</choice>magdalena</name> geynck vur<lb/>
den spiegel stayn Ind vlechde ir <choice><abbr>schoy̅</abbr><expan>schoyn</expan></choice> harr Ind zerrde<lb/>

yren licham<pc resp="editor">.</pc> Do sprach <name rend="underline" type="person" nymRef="Martha">martha</name> yrre <choice><abbr>sust<am>̛</am></abbr><expan>sust<ex>er</ex></expan></choice> zo myt cle<lb/>

glicher <choice><abbr>sty̅men</abbr><expan>stymmen</expan></choice><pc resp="editor">:</pc> <pc resp="editor">"</pc>alsus<pc source="manuscript">,</pc> leiff <choice><abbr>sust<am>̛</am></abbr><expan>sust<ex>er</ex></expan></choice> we zerrt ir uren<lb/>
licham also sere Ind ure <choice><abbr>schoy̅</abbr><expan>schoyn</expan></choice> sele de geschaffen is<lb/>
na deme gotlichen bylde<pc source="manuscript">,</pc> beuleckt ir myt <choice><abbr>ure̅</abbr><expan>uren</expan></choice> <choice><abbr>groesse̅</abbr><expan>groessen</expan></choice><lb/>

<choice><abbr>su̅den</abbr><expan>sunden</expan></choice><pc resp="editor">.</pc> Ich bydden uch <choice><abbr>my̅n</abbr><expan>myn</expan></choice> leve <choice><abbr>sust<am>̛</am></abbr><expan>sust<ex>er</ex></expan></choice> gedenckt dat<lb/>

ure lycham hait de <subst><del rend="strikethrough">schoinnt</del><add><unclear>schoynheit</unclear></add></subst> van der selen Ind dat <subst><del rend="strikethrough">dyn</del> <add>ure</add> </subst><choice><abbr>schoy̅</abbr><expan>schoyn</expan></choice><lb/>
licham dat ir zerrt myt goulde und myt syluer sal wer<lb/>

den <choice><abbr>ey̅</abbr><expan>eyn</expan></choice> spyse der woerme<pc resp="editor">!</pc><pc resp="editor">"</pc> Do antworde ir <name rend="underline" type="person" nymRef="Mary_Magdalene">maria</name>Ind sprach<pc resp="editor">:</pc><lb/>

<subst><add>Ind sprach</add></subst><pc resp="editor">"</pc><choice><abbr>my̅n</abbr><expan>myn</expan></choice> usserkoeren lieve <choice><abbr>sust<am>̛</am></abbr><expan>sust<ex>er</ex></expan></choice><pc resp="editor">.</pc> na dem dat ich<lb/>
also <choice><abbr>schoy̅</abbr><expan>schoyn</expan></choice> byn an myme licham Ind rych byn van ertz
</ab><pb/>
<pb edRef="#B1" facs="#B1_187r"/>
<ab>en goiden<pc source="manuscript">,</pc> so bydden ich dich bys zo vreden Ind lays mych<lb/>
myn goit <choice><abbr>ve<am>̛</am>tzeren</abbr><expan>vertzeren</expan></choice> myt vrouden myt den lieffhaveren deser<lb/>
werelt Ind lais uns nu zo samen vroelich syn<pc source="manuscript">,</pc> wer weyss<lb/>

we lange<pc resp="editor">.</pc><pc resp="editor">"</pc> Des <choice><abbr>andere̅</abbr><expan>anderen</expan></choice> dachs zoich <name rend="underline" type="person" nymRef="Mary_Magdalene"><choice><abbr>m<am>͂</am></abbr><expan>m<ex>aria</ex></expan>
</choice></name> zo huyss Ind<lb/>

<name rend="underline" type="person" nymRef="Martha">martha</name> schrey und <choice><abbr>wey̅de</abbr><expan>weynde</expan></choice> <choice><abbr>se<am>̛</am></abbr><expan>sere</expan></choice> dat ir <choice><abbr>sust<am>̛</am></abbr><expan>sust<ex>er</ex></expan></choice> so wylde was<pc resp="editor">.</pc></ab><lb/>

<ab xml:id="MaryMagdalene_lovers">Dar na <choice><abbr>ov<am>̛</am></abbr><expan>over</expan></choice> zwene maynde hatten de <choice><abbr>ju̅gelynck̅ne</abbr><expan>jungelynck</expan></choice> van <name rend="underline" type="place" nymRef="Jerusalem"><choice><abbr>jhrlm͂</abbr><expan>iherusalem</expan></choice></name><lb/>

eynen hoff Ind <choice><abbr>ey̅</abbr><expan>eyn</expan></choice> vroelicheit<pc source="manuscript">,</pc> dar zo wart <name rend="underline" type="person" nymRef="Mary_Magdalene"><choice><abbr>m<am>͂</am></abbr><expan>m<ex>aria</ex></expan>
</choice>magdalena</name><lb/>
gebeden Ind sy quam myt groesser kostlicht ind<lb/>
zerrheit irs lichams als <choice><abbr>ey̅</abbr><expan>eyn</expan></choice> <choice><abbr>lieffhau<am>̛</am>sche</abbr><expan>lieffhauersche</expan></choice> deser werelt Ind<lb/>
sprungen und dantzden ij dach Ind ij nacht so dat sy nau<lb/>
we spise nemen moicht van vroelicheit Ind wyldicheit<pc resp="editor">.</pc></ab><lb/>

<ab xml:id="market_scene">Ind in der <choice><abbr>selv<am>̛</am></abbr><expan>selver</expan></choice> zijt <choice><abbr>ve<am>̛</am>nam</abbr><expan>vernam</expan></choice> <name rend="underline" type="person" nymRef="Martha">martha</name> ir <choice><abbr>sust<am>̛</am></abbr><expan>sust<ex>er</ex></expan></choice> dat der <choice><abbr>he<am>̛</am></abbr><expan>here</expan></choice> <name rend="underline" type="person" nymRef="Jesus_Christ">jesus christus</name><lb/>
was in dem <name rend="underline" type="place" nymRef="Galilee">galileischen lande</name> Ind woulde er zo ir ko<lb/>

men zo <name rend="underline" type="place" nymRef="Bethany">bethanien</name><pc resp="editor">.</pc> Do geyncken <name rend="underline" type="person" nymRef="Martha">martha</name> Ind <name rend="underline" type="person" nymRef="Martilla">marcella</name><pc resp="editor">,</pc> de <name rend="underline" type="person" nymRef="Martha">marthen</name> mait<lb/>

was<pc resp="editor">,</pc> des morgens vroe in de stat <name rend="underline" type="place" nymRef="Jerusalem"><choice><abbr>jhrlm͂</abbr><expan>iherusalem</expan></choice></name> zo gelden spise<lb/>
vur den <name type="person" nymRef="Jesus_Christ">heren</name> Ind syn <choice><abbr>yu̅geren</abbr><expan>yungeren</expan></choice><pc source="manuscript">,</pc> so quamen sy van deme<lb/>

raytzhuiss myt pyfen und myt <choice><abbr>blasu̅gen</abbr><expan>blasungen</expan></choice><pc resp="editor">.</pc> <name rend="underline" type="person" nymRef="Mary_Magdalene">maria <choice><abbr>magdale̅a</abbr><expan>magdalena</expan></choice></name><lb/>

<choice><abbr>gey̅ck</abbr><expan>geynck</expan></choice> vur in deme rey myt <choice><abbr>hov<am>̛</am>dichen</abbr><expan>hoverdichem</expan></choice> hertzen<pc source="manuscript">,</pc> dyt<lb/>

sach <name rend="underline" type="person" nymRef="Martilla">marcella</name> dat <name rend="underline" type="person" nymRef="Mary_Magdalene"><choice><abbr>m<am>͂</am></abbr><expan>m<ex>aria</ex></expan>
</choice></name> geleyt wart in groessen eren ind<lb/>
vroelicheit<pc resp="editor">.</pc> Do saicht sy zo yrre vrauwen <name rend="underline" type="person" nymRef="Martha">martha</name><pc resp="editor">:</pc><lb/>

<pc resp="editor">"</pc>iunffer seyt ure <choice><abbr>sust<am>̛</am></abbr><expan>sust<ex>er</ex></expan></choice><pc resp="editor">!</pc><pc resp="editor">"</pc><pc source="manuscript">,</pc> do sach <name type="person" nymRef="Martha">martha</name> umb ind wart<lb/>

<choice><abbr>bitt<am>̛</am>lichen</abbr><expan>bitterlichen</expan></choice> <choice><abbr>schreye̅de</abbr><expan>schreyende</expan></choice> ind wranck ir hende zo <choice><abbr>same̅</abbr><expan>samen</expan></choice> ind<lb/>

sprach <choice><abbr>y̅ne̅clichen</abbr><expan>ynnenclichen</expan></choice><pc resp="editor">:</pc> <pc resp="editor">"</pc>O <choice><abbr>my̅</abbr><expan>myn</expan></choice> got ind <choice><abbr>my̅</abbr><expan>myn</expan></choice> schepper<pc resp="editor">,</pc>we wail<lb/>
dat mych noch tunckt dat <choice><abbr>my̅</abbr><expan>myn</expan></choice> <choice><abbr>sust<am>̛</am></abbr><expan>sust<ex>er</ex></expan></choice> gedeynt hat deme
</ab><pb/>
<pb edRef="#B1" facs="#B1_187v"/>
<ab>boesen geist<pc resp="editor">.</pc> nochtant bidden ich dich dattu sy anseyn<lb/>
wyls myt dynen <choice><abbr>bar̅hertzichen</abbr><expan>barmhertzichen</expan></choice> ougen ind gyff ir eynen<lb/>

<choice><abbr>andere̅</abbr><expan>anderen</expan></choice> <choice><abbr>sy̅ne</abbr><expan>synne</expan></choice> dat sy ir leuen bessen<pc resp="editor">!</pc><pc resp="editor">"</pc> Ind myt desen beden<lb/>

bleyff <name rend="underline" type="person" nymRef="Martha">martha</name> <choice><abbr>stay̅</abbr><expan>stayn</expan></choice> ind <choice><abbr>v<am>̛</am>leitte</abbr><expan>verleytte</expan></choice> na yrre <choice><abbr>sust<am>̛</am></abbr><expan>sust<ex>er</ex></expan></choice> <name rend="underline" type="person" nymRef="Mary_Magdalene">marien</name><pc resp="editor">.</pc><lb/>
Do <name rend="underline" type="person" nymRef="Mary_Magdalene"><choice><abbr>m<am>͂</am></abbr><expan>m<ex>aria</ex></expan>

</choice></name> quam zo yrre <choice><abbr>sust<am>̛</am></abbr><expan>sust<ex>er</ex></expan></choice><pc source="manuscript">,</pc> do sprach sy <name rend="underline" type="person" nymRef="Martha"><choice><abbr>marte̅</abbr><expan>marten</expan></choice></name> zo ind<lb/>
vraichde sy wat sy so vroe woulde ind wat sy so vroe<lb/>

in der stat dede<pc resp="editor">.</pc> <name rend="underline" type="person" nymRef="Martha">martha</name> de h<pc source="manuscript">.</pc> <choice><abbr>ju̅ffer</abbr><expan>junffer</expan></choice> antworde yr myt<lb/>
groessen <del rend="strikethrough">stat</del> oitmoidicht<pc source="manuscript">,</pc> dat sy were komen spise zo gelden<lb/>
vur eren gast<pc source="manuscript">,</pc> do en hatten de zwae neyt vyl wort<lb/>
zo samen umb des volcks wyllen dat da by <choice><abbr>stuy̅t</abbr><expan>stuynt</expan></choice><pc resp="editor">.</pc> Mer<lb/>
<name rend="underline" type="person" nymRef="Mary_Magdalene"><choice><abbr>m<am>͂</am></abbr><expan>m<ex>aria</ex></expan>

</choice></name> sprach myt lachendem munde<pc resp="editor">:</pc><pc resp="editor">"</pc> leiff <choice><abbr>sust<am>̛</am></abbr><expan>sust<ex>er</ex></expan></choice><pc resp="editor">,</pc> geilt ouch<lb/>
get vur mych ich wyl zo dir komen und wylle myt dir<lb/>

essen<pc resp="editor">.</pc><pc resp="editor">"</pc> her up spricht sent <name rend="underline" type="person" nymRef="Augustine">Augustinus</name><pc source="manuscript">,</pc> dat <name rend="underline" type="person" nymRef="Mary_Magdalene"><choice><abbr>m<am>͂</am></abbr><expan>m<ex>aria</ex></expan>
</choice></name> <choice><abbr>by̅ne̅</abbr><expan>bynnen</expan></choice> <choice><abbr>alle̅</abbr><expan>allen</expan></choice><lb/>
yren dagen ney bessen malzijten ass dan dese want he<lb/>

<ab>sy her ich wylle ir <choice><abbr>vru̅tlichen</abbr><expan>vruntlichen</expan></choice> zo sprechen<pc resp="editor">.</pc><pc resp="editor">"</pc> </ab> <ab xml:id="Gregory_comment">S Sanct <name type="person" nymRef="Gregory">Gre<lb/>
